adminPosition: Our creed, Discipline, Rules of Order, Belief and Doctrine is the word of God as taught and revealed by the Holy Spirit. (John 14:26, 1 Cor. 2:9-13). 'All Scripture is given by inspiration of God and is profitable for Doctrine, reproof, correction, instruction in righteousness; that the man of God may be perfect, thoroughly furnished unto all goo works' (II Tim. 3:16-17)
